title: 11/16/2020 - Best of The Herd
itunes:title: 11/16/2020 - Best of The Herd
description:
-The Seahawks couldn't win a game without Russell Wilson

-No reason to worry about Lamar Jackson losing to Belichick in a monsoon

-The Cardinals turnaround couldn't happen in any other sport

-Tom Brady got a huge break

-Where Colin was right, where Colin was wrong


Guest: Michael Vick, FOX Sports NFL Analyst
